title: Ep. 55 - Stop The Bailouts!
itunes:title: Stop The Bailouts!
description: Jeff Clark, expert trader from S&A, gives us the best way to play the collapse in Treasuries and rise in the dollar. Frank breaks down the markets and tells you why bailing out the PIIGS nations is a bad idea.
